<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  /* Success Green for completed action */
  .body { font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0fdf4; padding: 20px; }
  .card { max-width: 500px; background: #ffffff; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; }
  .header { background-color: #22c55e; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
  .content { padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.6; }
  .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
  .status-box { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px dashed #16a34a; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; color: #166534; font-size: 14px; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="body">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" width="100" alt="{{company}} Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 style="color: #166534;">Account Successfully Deleted</h2>
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>This email confirms that your <strong>{{company}}</strong> account has been officially closed.</p>
      <div class="status-box">
        <strong>Status:</strong> Your personal data and account history have been removed from our active systems. 
      </div>
      <p>We're sorry to see you go! If you ever change your mind, you’re welcome to create a new account anytime.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">Thank you for being part of our community. <br> © {{year}} {{company}}</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
